         <section id="benvortext">
            <paragraph xml-lang="en-US" id="par_id3155351" role="paragraph" l10n="CHG" oldref="2"><ahelp hid=".uno:StyleApply">Assigns a style to the current paragraph, selected paragraphs, or to a selected object.</ahelp></paragraph>
         </section>
      </section>
      <paragraph xml-lang="en-US" id="par_idN10621" role="paragraph" l10n="NEW">To reset the selected objects to the default paragraph style, select <emph>Clear formatting</emph>. Select <emph>More Styles</emph> to open the Styles and Formatting window.</paragraph>
      <paragraph xml-lang="en-US" id="par_idN10631" role="paragraph" l10n="NEW">By pressing the Down arrow button on the right of a style name, you show pop-up menu that allows to update style from selection or to edit style.</paragraph>
